	<li>Access to the electronic learning network</li>
	<li>Extensive peer and senior mentoring</li>
	<li>Business-sponsored activities and events that create opportunities to network with Bank&nbsp;of&nbsp;America Merrill Lynch professionals and summer associates across multiple business groups</li>
</ul>
</div></div>

